.name
Format
.author
Dave Schreiber
.description
A replacement for the Workbench 2.04 Format command.  It uses a much more
complete Workbench user interface (allowing for greater control over
formatting from Workbench) and issmaller than the original Format command.
.type
Workbench Tool
.version
1.00
.source
Full C source included.
.distribution
Copyright but Freely Redistributable
.requirements
Workbench/Kickstart 2.0 or later.
.short
Replacement for "format", V1.00, C src.
